These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: fanta, almond-milk, milk, juice
Pet: chinchilla, fish, ferret, pony
1. Pet:pony is on the left of Beverage:milk##1
2. Beverage:fanta is on the left of Pet:fish##1
3. Beverage:juice is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:ferret is on the left or right of Pet:pony##3
5. Beverage:fanta is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta | almond-milk | juice | milk |
| Pet        | chinchilla | fish   | pony | ferret    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: thriller, martial-arts, western, sports
Nationality: colombian, indian, chinese, american
1. Movie-Genre:martial-arts is on the left of Movie-Genre:sports##1
2. Nationality:colombian is on the left of Nationality:chinese##1
3. Nationality:chinese is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:colombian == Movie-Genre:thriller##1
5. Nationality:indian is on the right of Nationality:chinese##1
6. Nationality:colombian == Movie-Genre:thriller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | thriller  | martial-arts  | sports |
| Nationality   | american    | colombian | chinese | indian    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: corn, tomato, cranberry, peach
Movie-Genre: crime, thriller, action, drama
1. Food:peach is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:drama##3
2. Food:cranberry is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:drama is on the left or right of Food:tomato##3
4. Movie-Genre:drama is on the right of Movie-Genre:action##1
5. Movie-Genre:crime is in an odd position##4
6. Food:tomato is on the right of Food:cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | peach | cranberry | tomato    | corn      |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | drama     | crime | thriller |

