.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: collecting, video-games, magic-tricks, singing
Music-Genre: classical, salsa, soul, country
1. Hobby:video-games is between Music-Genre:classical and Music-Genre:country##2
2. Hobby:singing is on the left of Hobby:collecting##1
3. Music-Genre:soul is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:salsa is on the left of Music-Genre:country##1
5. Music-Genre:salsa is on the right of Hobby:collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | singing | collecting | video-games | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | soul       | classical   | salsa    | country  |

