.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, sprite, fanta
Music-Genre: metal, reggae, r&b, hip-hop
1. Beverage:iced-tea == Music-Genre:hip-hop##1
2. Music-Genre:metal is on the right of Beverage:iced-tea##1
3. Music-Genre:hip-hop is between Music-Genre:metal and Beverage:sprite##2
4. Beverage:iced-tea is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:hip-hop is on the left or right of Music-Genre:metal##3
6. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Music-Genre:reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate       | sprite   | iced-tea | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | reggae | hip-hop        | metal    |

