3. Beverage:cola is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:pumpkin is on the left of Food:lemon##1
5. Food:lemon is on the right of Beverage:soy-milk##1
6. Food:pumpkin is in an even position##4
7. Food:artichoke == Beverage:coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
